UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='The Burning Legion is in cahoots with Kael?  Hah!  Voren\'thal is going to have a field day with this information.$B$BDo you think the thousands of pilgrims that have come from Azeroth want to be allied with the Burning Legion?  I think not!', `VerifiedBuild`=26124 WHERE `ID`=10365; -- Shutting Down Manaforge Ara
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='It\'s about time you showed up.  I was beginning to wonder if the Scryers were interested at all.', `VerifiedBuild`=26124 WHERE `ID`=10202; -- A Defector
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You\'ve done well, $n.  Kael\'s army will not easily recover from the blow you\'ve dealt today.', `VerifiedBuild`=26124 WHERE `ID`=10341; -- Kick Them While They're Down
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='That makes three manaforges you\'ve shut down, $n.  Kael\'thas must be having a real fit right about now.', `VerifiedBuild`=26124 WHERE `ID`=10338; -- Shutting Down Manaforge Duro
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=66, `Emote2`=4, `Emote3`=2, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `EmoteDelay3`=1000, `RewardText`='$n!  Or, should I say Junior Technician 1st Grade $n?!  Oh hell, who am I kidding?  Skipping a grade isn\'t a good enough reward for what you\'ve done.  I\'m going to make you my first officer!$B$BYou\'ve saved all of us, and more importantly the X-52 Nether-Rocket!  I could just kiss you... but I won\'t.$B$BInstead, please let me present you with the gratitude of Area 52.  Take your pick!', `VerifiedBuild`=26124 WHERE `ID`=10249; -- Back to the Chief!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=15, `Emote2`=11, `RewardText`='Well, my $g boy : girl; that certainly was exciting!  And for my money, I\'d say that the Scrap Reaver X6000 performed admirably, despite its rookie pilot.$B$BHehe, no, don\'t take offense, I was just kidding.  After all, you just saved Area 52 and the X-52 Nether-Rocket from certain doom!', `VerifiedBuild`=26124 WHERE `ID`=10248; -- You, Robot
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `RewardText`='Well, well, it would appear that we are in luck, young $g man : lady;.$B$BI was just recently able to finish the construction of my latest invention, the Scrap Reaver X6000!$B$BAnd you\'re going to have the honor of helping me test it so that it can be used in defense of Area 52!', `VerifiedBuild`=26124 WHERE `ID`=10247; -- Doctor Vomisa, Ph.T.
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You do not cease to amaze me, $n.  That was quite the feat of stealth you pulled off at Manaforge Coruu.', `VerifiedBuild`=26124 WHERE `ID`=10200; -- Return to Thalodien
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=5, `Emote2`=1, `Emote3`=1, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `EmoteDelay3`=1000, `RewardText`='Heh, you\'re kidding, right?  The Burning Legion is blaming us for all of that?$B$BBut YOU\'RE the one that did it!$B$BOy, I have a headache and it\'s as big as this rocket.  Okay, okay, this calls for a change of plans.$B$BIf the Burning Legion thinks that it\'s going to come here, destroy our town and ruin my dream of cruising through the Twisted Nether, they are sadly mistaken.$B$BAnd I know just the goblin to help us out.', `VerifiedBuild`=26124 WHERE `ID`=10237; -- Warn Area 52!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Well, that\'s good and bad news, now isn\'t it?  We\'ve dealt them a blow, but with the Burning Legion running free all over the Netherstorm - and getting closer to us here - well, I don\'t know how it\'s going to go.$B$BI have a feeling that we\'re going to have to change gears here for a while.  Hope you\'ll be able to help us out, $n.', `VerifiedBuild`=26124 WHERE `ID`=10232; -- In A Scrap With The Legion
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `RewardText`='Well, I for one am glad that this petty little business is behind us.  I cannot remember a time when the Consortium has had dealings with such boorish and untrustworthy beings.$B$BYou, however, seem to be very trustworthy, $n.  Perhaps you wouldn\'t mind doing me one more favor?', `VerifiedBuild`=26124 WHERE `ID`=10267; -- Rightful Repossession
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<You describe the results of your scrying.>$B$BCommander Sarannis, you say? Hmm...$B$BShe\'s one of Kael\'thas\'s advisors, but certainly not a mage. I remember her from the attack on Kirin\'Var Village. I think your impressions are correct, $n. She\'s not maintaining the curse personally, but she holds the key to it.', `VerifiedBuild`=26124 WHERE `ID`=10256; -- Finding the Keymaster
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You have done well, $n. Destroying the dampening field will make it much easier for me to prepare the magic that will lift the tower\'s curse at last.', `VerifiedBuild`=26124 WHERE `ID`=10176; -- Ar'kelos the Guardian
