UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `RewardText`='<Mehrdad nods, then examines the diagnostic results.>$B$BThis is worrisome. The damage is much more severe than I believed. I can send to the Stormspire for some tools to begin repairs, but that\'s useless unless we\'ve isolated what\'s damaging the equipment in the first place.', `VerifiedBuild`=26124 WHERE `ID`=10417; -- Run a Diagnostic!
