UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Orik beams a smile at you.>$B$BYou did a good thing this day, $n. Hundreds of lost souls are now redeemed, thanks to you.', `VerifiedBuild`=26365 WHERE `ID`=12301; -- The Truth Shall Set Us Free
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Orik\'s eyes fill with tears.>$B$BThey don\'t know. None of them know! They think Arthas to be some great hero, when in truth it was Arthas who ordered the ships to be burned. It was Arthas who left us all for dead in this frozen wasteland!$B$B<Orik weeps.>$B$BNot all of the soldiers from the Prince\'s fleet perished in the freezing winter. I was only a lad when I was given the chance to battle the Scourge... to save our home from certain destruction. I took that chance, $n.', `VerifiedBuild`=26365 WHERE `ID`=12291; -- The Forgotten Tale
