UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='The slime is not natural, $n.  Its very nature is corrupt and... evil.$B$BWe must find out more.', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=12219; -- The Failed World Tree
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='It worked?$B$B<Raegar clears his throat.>$B$BI mean... of course it worked! This is incredible!$B$BYears from now, Explorers\' League initiates will hear the story of how Raegar Breakbrow, $n, and some hunk o\' junk golem defeated the thane of Dun Argol!', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=12153; -- The Iron Thane and His Anvil
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Could it be that Loken isn\'t really exaggerating? The titans\' stone and iron sons fighting against each other for control of the ancient city of Ulduar. This is madness, $n and it could destroy our only chance to learn the true history of dwarvenkind!', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=12185; -- Put on Your Best Face for Loken
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Kilian takes the uniform from you.>$B$BThis should do. I won\'t have time to sew on a little patch with \'$n\' embroidered on it or anything, but anyone looking closely at you should be convinced that you\'re an overseer by the time we\'re done with you.', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=12183; -- Looking the Part
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Don\'t do it, $n.  The people that sent you here.... you shouldn\'t trust them.', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=12300; -- Test of Mettle
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Katja reels away from you nervously.>$B$BThank you, $n.  You didn\'t get any wolfsbane on you, did you?  I\'ve got these... allergies that act up once in a while.', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=12307; -- Wolfsbane Root
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='It\'s good to finally meet you, $n!  We\'d heard about you up here.  Welcome to Silverbrook.$B$BThese trappers are a great bunch of lads and lasses.  Hardy people, they know the lay of the land really well.  You\'ll find it\'s a great thing that we finally won them over to our side.', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=12295; -- An Exercise in Diplomacy
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Good work, $n. I doubt any of the woodsmen would\'ve wanted to take a crack at the proto-drake, but we couldn\'t afford to let the Dragonflayers build a base of power in Grizzly Hills. If only the Horde was so easily dealt with...', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=12255; -- The Thane of Voldrune
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Well done, $n. Now, we must follow through and press the advantage.', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=12223; -- Thinning the Ranks
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Excellent news, $n.  With the locals\' help we\'ll have the logistical support we need to outmaneuver the Horde in this region.$B$BI have further tasks for you if you\'re interested.', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=12294; -- A Tentative Pact
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Nice work, $n.  We could use a few more folks like you up here.  We could really show the Horde not to mess with us.', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=12444; -- Blackriver Skirmish
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `RewardText`='Well done, $n! Without their leader, the Horde is weak and disorganized. I will order our men forward.', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=12314; -- Down With Captain Zorna!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Good to see that you survived that impact. Quite the explosion!$b$bWe can\'t afford for the Horde to make off with all that lumber.$b$bWell done, $c.', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=12437; -- Riding the Red Rocket
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Ahh yes. That\'ll save me hours.$b$bTake this for your trouble, friend. And keep an eye out for more element 115. I\'ll take all you can find.', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=12443; -- Seeking Solvent
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=113, `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=12323; -- Smoke 'Em Out
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=12316; -- Keep Them at Bay!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You\'ve done well in felling Megalith, but I wonder about his final words.$B$BYou\'re sure he said the Stoneforge?$B$BI know of no place with that name, but it sounds like a word with origins in the titans. What plans do the Iron Dwarves have for such a thing? This bears watching, $n, for we must find it before the Iron Dwarves\' plan comes to fruition.', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=11359; -- Demolishing Megalith
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='At last, we can finally fish in peace! \'Course, by the time we catch anything, the expedition\'ll arrive and claim it all for themselves.$B$BYou have our thanks, $n. Don\'t be a stranger \'round here.', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=11410; -- The One That Got Away
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<The priest quietly mouths a benediction for you.>$B$BBless you, $n, you have answered my prayers. Stand proudly in the Light, chin held high with the knowledge that your actions were most holy!$B$BI\'m certain that the church\'s coffers can yield up something of use to you.', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=11239; -- In Service to the Light
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<The captain breathes a sigh of relief.>$B$BWell, that should take some of the pressure off of us.$B$B$n, time and again you have proven yourself invaluable to Westguard Keep and the Alliance at large. Pick something from the treasury, $g boy : girl;! It\'s the least we can do!', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=11236; -- Necro Overlord Mezhen
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You did what had to be done. Though some might consider it dishonorable to slay the helpless, in this case you would have been a fool to have done otherwise.$B$BAnd we certainly couldn\'t have just left them standing there to be ritually wakened, now could we?$B$BIt was a brave thing you did for all of us down in those catacombs, $n.', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=11432; -- Sleeping Giants
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Wow, that horn is cold!$B$BOnce again you\'ve saved Westguard Keep from certain doom. What a curious $g man : woman; you are, $n. If only there were more of you.$B$BWell, this certainly calls for a reward. Which do you prefer?', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=11238; -- The Frost Wyrm and its Master
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Good work, $n, and good riddance.$B$BBut, what you say about that place troubles me still, and I think our culling is not quite at an end!', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=11235; -- Dealing With Gjalerbron
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='$n, we can\'t let this come to pass!', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=11237; -- Gjalerbron Attack Plans
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='That\'s unbelievably good news! I knew that you could pull it off, $n!$B$BAt least someone around here can produce results!$B$BWell, this calls for a reward. Go ahead, take your pick; the treasury is open to you.', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=11250; -- All Hail the Conqueror of Skorn!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Nicely done, $n, nicely done!$B$B<The captain seems beside himself with glee.>$B$BThat\'ll show those good-for-nothing Forsaken to think about messing with us!$B$BI\'d say you\'ve earned yourself something from the treasury!', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=11332; -- Mission: Plague This!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Yes, $n, what is it now?$B$BWHAT?!! A Forsaken super plague that melts you in no time?$B$BYou oozed my vrykul prisoner?$B$B<The captain looks almost sad and spits in disgust.>$B$BAlright, I know what we need to do. Or rather, what YOU need to do!', `VerifiedBuild`=26822 WHERE `ID`=11331; -- You Tell Him ...Hic!

