UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=66, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `RewardText`='I commend you, $n. These centaur are undisciplined and cannot focus their rage as the orcs can, but they are fierce nonetheless.  In defeating them, your valor is proven.', `VerifiedBuild`=30706 WHERE `ID`=852; -- Hezrul Bloodmark
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=2, `RewardText`='Thank you, $n. Studying the beasts of an area can tell much about the area itself. We shall see what tale these shells tell, and possibly unravel the mystery of what\'s happening in the barrens.$B$BPlease accept my gratitude for your aid... and perhaps you can use these coins. I find that I do not need them.', `VerifiedBuild`=30706 WHERE `ID`=880; -- Altered Beings
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=5, `RewardText`='Your findings are amazing! Jerrik was wise to send you there. We now know that whatever rests under these oases can create life from nothing! No doubt this is causing the havoc to the south, but my primary concern right now is preserving the balance up here.$B$BWe must study this more...', `VerifiedBuild`=30706 WHERE `ID`=877; -- The Stagnant Oasis
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='So you\'ve been to the nests and placed the feathers of your prey within them. That took a fair portion of courage, no doubt about it.$B$BDo you feel a little tougher, $n? Because you look tougher now then when you first came here.  I guess the Barrens is doing its job.', `VerifiedBuild`=30706 WHERE `ID`=905; -- Into the Raptor's Den
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You did it! That\'ll really upset the balance of power down here. Verog left no clear successor, so I expect this crew of brutes will fall on each other like hungry dogs. I\'ll stay here and keep an eye on what happens next.$B$BVerog answered directly to the Kolkar Chief - killing him is a good start, but there\'s more work to be done.', `VerifiedBuild`=30706 WHERE `ID`=851; -- Verog the Dervish
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='You\'ve beaten Echeyakee, and though his days of hunting are over... his spirit is with you. He will show you the strength found in subtlety, and the honor in mercy.$B$BI underestimated you, $c. The Horde is fortunate to have you in its ranks.', `VerifiedBuild`=30706 WHERE `ID`=881; -- Echeyakee
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=462, `RewardText`='Ah, yes. These are good specimens. Potent.$B$BI am Forsaken, and we honor our contracts. Here is your reward, $n.', `VerifiedBuild`=30706 WHERE `ID`=848; -- Fungal Spores
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=6, `RewardText`='You found a fissure in the earth, with power emanating from it? Strange. Something is causing that oasis to bubble over suddenly with life.$B$BCome, $c - there is something else I\'d like you to investigate with me.', `VerifiedBuild`=30706 WHERE `ID`=870; -- The Forgotten Pools
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='Ah, I see you\'ve been busy. I hope you learned a lot from this prey, $n. You\'ll need the strength and cunning of beasts like these to serve my beloved Horde.', `VerifiedBuild`=30706 WHERE `ID`=903; -- Hunting the Huntress
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='Not bad, $n. Those zhevra hold a lot of strength in their legs. I\'ve seen them knock even a tauren on its haunches!$B$BIt looks like you have some strength in you too.', `VerifiedBuild`=30706 WHERE `ID`=845; -- The Zhevra
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='Well done, $n. Kodobane is just one strand of a tangled thread - there are other Kolkar leaders to kill elsewhere in the Barrens. Seek out my companions at the other oases if you wish to press the assault.', `VerifiedBuild`=30706 WHERE `ID`=850; -- Kolkar Leaders
