UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=66, `Emote2`=1, `RewardText`='It\'s bad enough to have one\'s village sacked... but to spend the following night in a quilboar cage? I\'m glad you were there to help, $n.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=24529; -- Bad to Worse
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=273, `Emote2`=1, `RewardText`='So it is done.$B$BNormally these scavengers are part of the Earthmother\'s cycle of life. But on the heels of the devastation wracked by both the Alliance and the cataclysm, their numbers grow overwhelming. It is good to thin them out.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=24525; -- Keeping the Dogs at Bay
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=5, `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=27472; -- Rise, Godfrey
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `Emote3`=1, `RewardText`='I had no doubt that you would succeed, $n. I hope you can understand why I kept the true purpose of your mission a secret. Should Crowley and Bloodfang have found out about our plan, they would have surely gotten to Godfrey first and disposed of the body.$B$BStand by, $n. The time of their rebirth is at hand.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=27438; -- The Great Escape
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `RewardText`='Here we are, $n. He is a little rotted, but no worse for the wear. We must hurry before the Alliance finds us!', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=27406; -- A Man Named Godfrey
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=274, `Emote2`=1, `RewardText`='No time to bask in the battle glory, $n. We have a job to do. I have no doubt more of those beasts are on the way.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=27423; -- Resistance is Futile
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `RewardText`='Forward Commander Onslaught fought until the bitter end, $n. It took a pack of bloodthirsty worgen to finally bring him down. We must not let his death, or the death of all of our soldiers in Gilneas, go in vain. Our mission MUST succeed.$B$BNow I will reveal to you why we are here.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=27405; -- Fall Back!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Though we were shamed in battle, the enemy was not victorious. I will not soon forget this, $n.$B$BIf I make it back to Silverpine I will likely retire from the service. War is not in my blood.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=27360; -- Vengeance for Our Soldiers
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<The F.C.D. crackles with electricity.>$B$BAn Alliance armada is en route? How could this have happened?$B$B<Forward Commander Onslaught cuts out for a moment. You hear worgen howling in the background.>$B$BYou\'ve got to hurry, $n. We\'re being overrun up here at Forward Command.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=27364; -- On Whose Orders?
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<The F.C.D. crackles with static.>$B$BDreadwatch is lost? This is bad, $n. Real bad.$B$BIf Dreadwatch is compromised it means we\'ve lost Gilneas City.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=27349; -- Break in Communications: Dreadwatch Outpost
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='If I could still breathe I\'d let out a sigh of relief.$B$BDon\'t get too comfortable, though, $n, your mission here has just begun.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=27333; -- Losing Ground
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Well if it isn\'t $nnub!$B$BI hope you\'re ready for battle, because that\'s all you\'ll find in this hellhole. We\'re at the heart of contested territory and these worgen mongrels won\'t give an inch!', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=27290; -- To Forsaken Forward Command
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<The Banshee Queen\'s voice invades your thoughts.>$B$BYou have avenged the fallen, $n, but there is more to be done.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=27181; -- Excising the Taint
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Though you killed a large number of the newly turned worgen, many more are sure to appear. Still, their assault will have softened. Well done, $n!', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=27232; -- The Waters Run Red...
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=21, `RewardText`='Bloody well done!  Right-o!  Congratulations, $n, for succeeding where others have failed.$b$bI am honored to count you as a comrade of our great hunting party here.  No one will ever doubt your expertise in hunting and tracking!$b$bCheers to you, I say!  Cheers!', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=208; -- Big Game Hunter
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=21, `RewardText`='So the great Bhag\'thera is dead!  Cheers to you, $n.  You are a mighty $c indeed!', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=193; -- Panther Mastery
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=21, `RewardText`='Most impressive, I do say!  I send you out to defeat the kittens, and you return with a paw the size of a gnome!  You are a true Master Tiger Hunter, $n!', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=188; -- Tiger Mastery
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=6, `RewardText`='$G Master : Mistress; $n, the raptor slayer!$b$bHas a nice ring to it, eh?', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=197; -- Raptor Mastery
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=21, `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=192; -- Panther Prowess
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=21, `RewardText`='You have defeated the strongest tigers in Stranglethorn.  You have become a great tiger hunter, and have every right to stop your hunt right here and now.$b$bSomething tells you, however, that a stronger cat still waits for you within that jungle...', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=187; -- Tiger Prowess
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=21, `RewardText`='You are no longer just a raptor hunter.  You are an honest-to-goodness raptor SLAYER.$b$bThough one fabled raptor still eludes you...', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=196; -- Raptor Prowess
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=21, `RewardText`='Hemet Nesingwary Jr. doubted you, but his doubts were unfounded.  You are absolutely destroying these raptors.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=195; -- Raptor Stalking
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=21, `RewardText`='Tiger blood coats your hands, your weapons, and your $c garb.  Yet still you crave more.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=186; -- Tiger Stalking
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=21, `RewardText`='Stranglethorn raptors were not a problem for a wily $c like you.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=194; -- Raptor Hunting
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=21, `RewardText`='You take a moment to silently congratulate yourself on your panther hunting so far.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=191; -- Panther Stalking
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=21, `RewardText`='You have finished with the young tigers... but the thrill of the hunt still holds you captive.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=185; -- Tiger Hunting
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=21, `RewardText`='You feel more experienced already.  Perhaps it\'s time to move on to bigger prey.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=190; -- Panther Hunting
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=2, `Emote2`=1, `Emote3`=1, `RewardText`='Jolly nice to make your acquaintance, $n.  Haven\'t seen a $c around these parts for some time.$b$bI\'ve one purpose in being here: to hunt a great and elusive beast.  Seeing that you\'re a hero of sorts I am willing to let you take part in the hunt, but you must first prove yourself.$b$bI shall teach the ways of raptor killing to you.  Ajeck will train you with tiger hunting.  And Sir Erlgadin is a master of panther tracking.$b$bProve your skill and I\'ll let you in on the big hunt.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=583; -- Welcome to the Jungle
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='I can feel the raw power contained in this gem, $n. I\'ll send it to Silvermoon for our magisters to study further, but I am sure it will prove useful in our struggle against the Amani.$B$BYour help has been invaluable in procuring this gem, and I will see to it that the Farstriders know the name of the $r who made this find possible.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=9457; -- An Unusual Patron
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='Well done. Now, this is curious...$B$BThe inscription on this totem is in a language no troll could ever hope to learn, but one that is known to us. It names the bearer as an ally of a water elemental named Naias and marks him as one worthy to channel his power.$B$BThis is most unexpected, but not entirely bad, $n. With your help, I\'d like to pursue this further.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=9436; -- Bloodscalp Insight
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=4, `RewardText`='Stinky was here with the herbs I ask of him, and he told me you helped him out of a bind.  Good work!  A friend of Stinky\'s is a friend of mine!$B$BHe asked me to give you this if I ever saw you, right before he walked back south toward the marsh.', `VerifiedBuild`=32305 WHERE `ID`=1270; -- Stinky's Escape
