UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Lok\'tar ogar! I have heard much about you, $n. Your battle scars run deep - a testament to your dedication and power!$B$BWith the flanking attacks of the Lich King crushed in both the west and east, only the forces at the gate remain. We gain ground each day, soon to break through this wall and into Icecrown!$B$BOnce we stop the skeletal dragons, Highlord Fordragon and I will take the field.', `VerifiedBuild`=32750 WHERE `ID`=12224; -- The Kor'kron Vanguard!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Doctor Malefious looks through the contents of the package.>$B$BGlorious! Exactly to specifications!$B$BHere is your payment, $n. Keep what you\'ve seen and done to yourself. This work is all classified - information is given out on a need to know basis.', `VerifiedBuild`=32750 WHERE `ID`=12221; -- The Forsaken Blight
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Let\'s see them bring her back to life without her head!$B$B<The high executor\'s laugh draws a number of furtive glances.>$B$BI\'m a little concerned that you let this grand admiral get away, but you\'re still the $g hero : heroine; of the day, $n!$B$BTake your pick... you\'ve earned it!', `VerifiedBuild`=32750 WHERE `ID`=12285; -- Do Unto Others
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<You think you see just the hint of a smile cross Wroth\'s face before quickly disappearing.>$B$BYou\'re now my favorite $c, $n. If you have a mind to, I\'d like you to think about joining up as an officer in the Hand of Vengeance.$B$BWe can start you out as a deathguard, and in a few decades I think you have what it takes to make junior executor!$B$BNo? Well don\'t be too hasty... take your time and mull it over.', `VerifiedBuild`=32750 WHERE `ID`=12273; -- The Denouncement
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='I knew my sister wouldn\'t let us down.$B$BWell done, $n. The Onslaught\'s lumbermill will be out of commission for a while, which means no new construction or ballistae.$B$BThanks for helping me to live up to the family name.', `VerifiedBuild`=32750 WHERE `ID`=12240; -- A Means to an End
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='What? You were expecting us to have you rescue them?$B$BNow why would we do that when they have a proven track record of getting themselves captured in the first place?$B$BNorthrend is a cold place, young $n. I suggest that you adjust to it.', `VerifiedBuild`=32750 WHERE `ID`=12245; -- No Mercy for the Captured
