UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Excellent. Just as I suspected all along. I shall have to attempt to contact Ysera and see if she approves.$B$BIf she can be coaxed from her nightmare, of course.$B$BThank you, $n. You have been indispensable.', `VerifiedBuild`=32750 WHERE `ID`=12459; -- That Which Creates Can Also Destroy
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Oh my goodness, you made it! I was uncertain.$B$BYou flickered in and out of the time stream there for a moment during the fight! I thought for sure that we\'d lost you!$B$BBut here you are safe and sound, with your past self rescued, on the other side of the time loop you were in.$B$BYou\'re quite the temporal $g hero : heroine;, $n!', `VerifiedBuild`=32750 WHERE `ID`=13343; -- Mystery of the Infinite, Redux
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You saw Nozdormu? That doesn\'t make any sense.$B$B<Chromie thinks a moment about what you\'ve said.>$B$BActually, that\'s great news! We had no idea of where or when the Lord of Time had gone to. We just knew that he had disappeared to deal with very important matters.$B$BSo, even though the leader of the Infinite Dragonflight wasn\'t revealed, you\'ve discovered that Nozdormu is alive and well, and fighting back against them!$B$BThank you, $n. I\'ll be seeing you soon!', `VerifiedBuild`=32750 WHERE `ID`=12470; -- Mystery of the Infinite
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You must be $n. The queen informed me that you would be coming.$B$BIf you are willing, we are in great need of your assistance.', `VerifiedBuild`=32750 WHERE `ID`=12435; -- Report to Lord Afrasastrasz
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Back so soon, $n?$B$BVargastrasz sent word ahead of you. Thank you for what you did at the Ruby Dragonshrine.', `VerifiedBuild`=32750 WHERE `ID`=12769; -- The Steward of Wyrmrest Temple
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You must be $n. I was told you\'d be coming.$B$B<The ambassador grunts.>$B$BI have something that I want you to take care of. If you do, you\'ll prove yourself to the dragons here.', `VerifiedBuild`=32750 WHERE `ID`=12767; -- Speak with your Ambassador
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='HA! You did it! The soldiers at the Wrathgate are indebted to you, $n! This\'ll surely buy a few of them another day above ground.', `VerifiedBuild`=32750 WHERE `ID`=12097; -- Sarathstra, Scourge of the North
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You spoke with Oacha\'noa?!$B$BIf it is her will that we stand with your people then so be it. Elder Ko\'nani will accept this as our destiny, for weal or woe.$B$BMy people believe that all souls are one with the magic of the world. We must oppose the blue dragon attempts to control the magic or we are all doomed!$B$BI never thought that a $r would be the champion of the Kalu\'ak, but you have proven me wrong. On behalf of my people, I give you thanks, $n.$B$BMay the gods smile upon you and keep you safe.', `VerifiedBuild`=32750 WHERE `ID`=12032; -- Conversing With the Depths
