(47952, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Keep your eyes open. I\'m not sure we\'re entirely welcome.', 27980), -- The Missing Fleet
(52148, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Gotta admit, when I first saw you in that prison cell I wasn\'t sure what all the fuss was about.\n\nBut you really came through for me. You came through for everyone.\n\nThanks, mate.', 27980), -- Freehold: A Pirate's End
(53074, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Excellent. Your new recruits will be available for missions once they have finished their training.', 27980), -- Reinforcements
(51715, 273, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I am sure Falstad will handle this mission with his usual grace.', 27980), -- War of Shadows
(51568, 4, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Good work! These look great!$b$bThese bars will be used as part of our next warship.$b$bNow then, you scratched my back, and I will scratch yours. Storm silver is very brittle naturally. When you mine it, use several small swings instead of one big one. That\'ll keep the metal from being chipped away.', 27980), -- Ritualistic Preparations
(48752, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Thanks! You can never be too careful when it comes to breathing thick clouds of smoke from burning coal and molten metal.$b$bNow I owe you a lesson about monelite. Let\'s see, what to teach...$b$bWhen you\'re mining monelite, instead of chipping away at the rock, try using the pick to pierce the metal, and pull all of it away from the rock like it was taffy.', 27980), -- A Need For Coal
(50249, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'We finally got some useful information from him?', 27980), -- A Boralus Triple Threat
(49734, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Good work. That should be enough help to get my men back in that fort and manning it again.', 27980), -- Targeting a Turncoat
(49716, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A grim task, but one that needed to be done.', 27980), -- A Lesson on Trust
(49720, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'My birds deserve better partners than men who betray their own country.', 27980), -- Free Bird
(49733, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'My gratitude, that should help alleviate some of the soldiers\' pain.', 27980), -- Patching Up the Rear
(51226, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'There\'s one problem dealt with.', 27980), -- Death from Two Sides
(49715, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A courier? I think we lost him in the coup.', 27980), -- Trouble at Greystone Keep
(49302, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'My inadequacy to rule lead to Deepwarden\'s near takeover of not only the fishing operation here, but the village as a whole.$b$bI can no longer allow myself to sit quietly and allow people like him to walk over me to do as they please! I\'ve learned that, thanks to you.', 27980), -- The Deadliest Catch
(48370, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Perhaps now the danger may come to an end.', 27980), -- Death in the Depths
(48372, 6, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Is this truly the end?', 27980), -- Eldritch Invocations
(48368, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The screams have subsided, if ever slightly.', 27980), -- Deep Sea Defilement
(48367, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'It\'s best to not know what corrupted eggs will hatch into, though I could imagine the fight that we may now never see.', 27980), -- Those Aren't Fish Eggs
(48366, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'From here, we can launch our investigation.', 27980), -- Paddle to Safety
(49719, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Here\'s your pay. You seem suited for the Roughneck life. Come back sometime if you need work.', 27980), -- Getting Paid
(49419, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Whank woo!', 27980), -- Frozen
(49431, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ooooh, that\'s nice. Real nice. Hop in if you want, the water is great! Ignore the bubbles.', 27980), -- Warm and Cozy
(49433, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This\'ll help protect my boys down the hill. Well done.', 27980), -- Wendies
(49439, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'To survive out here, we do what we have to. Today that meant avenging members of the pack.$B$BThank you for your help. If you ever need anything, don\'t hesitate to call on the Roughnecks.', 27980), -- Boss' Revenge
(49435, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Pity. At least I can tell the rest of the boys they went down fighting.', 27980), -- Where'd They Go?
(49418, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You the new kid? Frankly, it doesn\'t matter. I got a problem and you\'re going to help me with it.', 27980), -- Big Boss
(49417, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I can\'t believe you did it, kid! I knew you\'d be Roughneck material!', 27980), -- Roughneck Riders
(49710, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The eggs fit nicely into the new nest.', 27980), -- An Offering of Eggs
(49735, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Bloody saurolisks. Good riddance.', 27980), -- Protect the Nests
(49395, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You got more on your shirt than you got in the bottles! I\'d ask you to shower, but frankly none of us have done that in weeks.', 27980), -- The Bears and the Bees
(51368, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The hornet\'s dead! Good on ya, house cat.\n\nI\'d like to not die to a bug.', 27980), -- WANTED: The Hornet
(49394, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You actually did it! Tell me, how did they like it? Any of \'em give you the horns? Hahaha!', 27980), -- Hold Still
(49412, 4, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Thanks so much! I\'m off to my next task!', 27980), -- Helping Henry
(49393, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Here for the job are ye? Well buckle up house cat, it gets rough from here on out.', 27980), -- The Roughnecks
(51384, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Aye, you got the saurok.\n\nBilge Rats should be out of here soon enough.', 27980), -- WANTED: Quartermaster Ssylis
(48009, 396, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You did what needed to be done.', 27980), -- Betrayal of the Guard
(48365, 396, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<Alby clears his throat.>$b$bIt is good to see the young lord safe.$b$b...Thanks.', 27980), -- The Young Lord Stormsong
(48356, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This has never been a simple illness. There is foul magic at work here.', 27980), -- Possessive Headgear
(48008, 396, 0, 0, 0, 300, 0, 0, 0, 'All we can do now is try to contain the threat.', 27980), -- Dangerous Cargo
(49299, 396, 0, 0, 0, 300, 0, 0, 0, 'Bates gave everything he had for greater power. Shame it had to go that way.', 27980), -- Enemy Within
(48354, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I am... aghast. How could this happen right under our very noses?', 27980), -- Tainted Shipments
(48355, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'If there is even a chance of harm to innocents, we must protect them at all cost.', 27980), -- Evacuate the Premises
(48353, 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'In the name of the sea! Did you see that?', 27980), -- Pulse of the Wharf
(49292, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'In all my days, I have never seen such an illness. We must find the source!', 27980), -- Algae Shakes
(48348, 4, 1, 0, 0, 0, 300, 0, 0, 'Well throw me a hammer and call me Nancy!$b$bThank you kindly pal. This should be plenty! I\'ll get to work!', 27980), -- Stinging Barbs
(49268, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Unfortunate... the tides still speak the same.', 27980), -- Sharks in the Water
(48352, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Glorious! This should be plenty.', 27980), -- A Cure from the Sea
(48540, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'No seaweed? This will not do at all!', 27980), -- Aiding the Wharf
(48347, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Oh! Are you here because of my posting?$b$bThank the sea, I need all the able-bodied help I can get.', 27980), -- Anglepoint Wharf
(51367, 4, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You defeated the revenant! Bully! Well done as always, my friend!', 27980), -- WANTED: Raging Earthguard
(47755, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'My men have been reporting back to me. Thanks for freeing them, $n.', 27980), -- Captured and Enraptured
(50005, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You found my precious little sea star!', 27980), -- Hold My Hand
(50059, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I decided if you can\'t beat \'em, join \'em! That one over there looks available. Think she\'ll go out with me?$B$BOh, and thanks for getting everyone back at their posts. We got a lot of cleanup.', 27980), -- Can't Hear A Thing
(50002, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Who are you? Where\'s my dad? I\'m hungry. Can I have a sword? Where\'s my dad?!', 27980), -- A Very Precious Cargo
(50026, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'We need your help, sailor!', 27980), -- Save Our Shipmates
(48903, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'He\'s on! He\'s on!$b$bDon\'t worry, $n. I\'m sure he\'ll be fine! Thanks for all of your help!', 27980), -- The Perfect Horse, of Course
(48898, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I think I can feel the luck too!', 27980), -- Lucky Charm
(48902, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Oh boy oh boy! He\'s gonna be pumped!', 27980), -- Monstrous Energy
(48899, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ah yes, these shells will help keep me well safeguarded!', 27980), -- Safety First
(49036, 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'What a showing!', 27980), -- Best In Show
(48089, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 300, 0, 0, 'Our people defend the estate with renewed vigor!', 27980), -- Mountain Sounds
(48088, 1, 11, 0, 0, 0, 300, 0, 0, 'A grand showing! You had me on the edge of my seat!', 27980), -- No Party Like a Trogg Party
