(48939, 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'What a showing!', 27980), -- Show Me What You've Got
(48004, 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Well done, $n! I think you\'re ready to take it to the next level!', 27980), -- Beginner Equitation
(48005, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'How are you enjoying the grounds? We are still setting up, so it will be even more marvelous soon!$b$bTo tell you the truth, I have to one-up myself every year. It\'s quite exhausting organizing it all, but it\'s so very rewarding!', 27980), -- Be Our Guest
(48003, 1, 11, 0, 0, 0, 300, 0, 0, 'You\'re $n? The hero that saved my son from the troggs?$b$bHohoho! You are very welcome at my estate! You must regale me with your tales of your gallant rescue!', 27980), -- The Lord's Behest
(48597, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Troggs training saurolisks to be ridden? Seems they\'ve learned from watching us after all.$b$bIt\'s better that you freed them. I don\'t particularly want to imagine what would happen if the troggs were widely successful in their new riding endeavors!', 27980), -- Saurolisk Escape
(48195, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Fewer troggs means fewer of our people getting attacked.', 27980), -- Troublesome Troglodytes
(48778, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The soup has somehow taken on a somewhat floral quality. It feels well-balanced on the tongue and goes down very smoothly.$b$bThis may be, in fact, the most delicious cuisine you have ever tasted.', 27980), -- Stone Soup
(48196, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You saved me! Those troggs are really scary. They took Hotshot and dragged me through their camp!', 27980), -- Following Eddie's Trail
(48670, 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'How could this get any worse?$b$bThe troggs have captured Eddie!', 27980), -- Runaway Rider
(48965, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<Caleb\'s body is lifeless, still warm. His wounds claimed him while you were gone.$b$bHis face seems content, as though he knew you would finish the job.>', 27980), -- Settle the Score
(48077, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Not only will these pelts please the nobles, they also prove your worth as a hunter.', 27980), -- The Stoat Hunt
(48616, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'There\'s nothing like man and beast working together for a clean hunt!', 27980), -- Bolas and Birds
(48080, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<Harold lets out a hardy laugh.>$b$bNow that\'s what I\'m talking about!', 27980), -- An Element of Danger
(48070, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Welcome, traveler! Care to join in the hunt?', 27980), -- The Norwington Festival
(52258, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Oooh! These are so pretty! I bet they\'ll sell really well.', 27980), -- She Sells Seashells
(49229, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I\'ve fought off spirits afore, but ne\'er the actual ruins themselves.', 27980), -- The Ruins Fought Back
(49234, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I heard the falling of stone echo through the cave from here. Nice work.', 27980), -- A Marine Out of Water
(49260, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Everything worth our attention should be stored in my bag, many thanks.', 27980), -- Backup While I Pack Up
(49225, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Yer here to help? Finally!', 27980), -- Chasing the Leader
(49233, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Another victory for druid magic! This staff is much more effective than any of Cranklefuse\'s gadgets.', 27980), -- I'm a Druid, Not a Priest
(49232, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I can\'t wait to see what sort of power I can squeeze out of these.', 27980), -- Salvaging a Disaster
(51151, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'We might have a wee problem on our hands.', 27980), -- A Letter to the League
(49467, 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<Maynard studies the locket.>$b$bThat ungrateful woman!', 27980), -- Witch of the Woods
(49450, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I have never seen beasts so... soulless. It\'s as if they\'re under some sort of spell.', 27980), -- Incident Reports
(49454, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Thanks for that.$b$bI uh... I think you got some spider egg goop on your cloak.', 27980), -- Pest Prevention
(49468, 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A witch?! This is all because of a witch?!', 27980), -- Required Webinar
(50058, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<With the spider matriarch defeated, the flow of cursed spiders should slow, if not stop completely.>', 27980), -- The Witch's Pet
(48369, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Father is blinded in his pursuit of success. If he won\'t listen to our employees, I must!', 27980), -- Emergent Strategy
(49451, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'My son is far too soft-hearted. He needs to harden up if he\'s going to run this business one day!', 27980), -- Time Off Requests
(49452, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Perhaps the cost of the axes should come out of their paychecks from now on!', 27980), -- Inventory Deficit
(49465, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<Algerson examines the skull.>$b$bNow this... this is something! Why are my workers running, they should be harvesting!$b$bWe could make a killing with these!', 27980), -- Maximizing Resources
(48557, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Algerson\'s greed may have hurt this land, but it can still be saved.', 27980), -- Sowing Saplings
(49453, 4, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Hooray! Now the beavers will be safe from the lumberjacks and the spiders!', 27980), -- Give a Dam
(50699, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Why hello! Welcome to Algerson Lumber. How may I help you?', 27980), -- Worker's Rights
(51358, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I heard the lost gryphon came back!\n\nI guess we\'ve got you to thank, $n.', 27980), -- WANTED: Gryphon 'Nappers
(51144, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ah, my furs! Thanks for the delivery. It\'s getting a bit cold out here - these will be perfect for the beds!$b$bIf you need food or a place to lay your head, I can offer you the best!', 27980), -- A Bundle of Furs
(49523, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Hmm. A scam, was it? You have my apologies for putting you in harm\'s way.$B$BThis man should be delivered to justice. He may be in hiding now, but I am very, very patient.', 27980), -- A Bad Deal
(47962, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Even under normal circumstances, the tidesages would be wary of outsiders. I\'ll accompany you on this mission and maybe we can finally get some answers.', 27980), -- Stormsong Valley
(50972, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'So, Katherine is willing to speak with us at last?$B$BWell done.', 27980), -- Proudmoore's Parley
(51569, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A fine choice, $n.', 27980), -- The Zandalar Campaign
(51570, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You have chosen to sail to Zuldazar.', 27980), -- Foothold: Zuldazar
(51714, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Good, we\'re all here. I asked for you by name, $n. Falstad as well.', 27980), -- Mission from the King
(53332, 273, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<Halford looks over the gathered resources.>\n\nThis should do it.', 27980), -- Time for War
(50790, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I don\'t know how anyone could survive a fall like that.$B$BStill, we should be careful not to let our guard down.', 27980), -- Hot Pursuit
(50789, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<The last of the civilians escape to safety as the smoke clears.>', 27980), -- Clear the Air
(50788, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<The Proudmoore Guard can mop things up from here.>', 27980), -- Enemies Within
(50787, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Damnit! Where\'d she go?!', 27980), -- Make Our Case
(50795, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Alright. It\'s time.', 27980), -- Prepare for Trouble
(50110, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'It seems word of the attack has already reached Boralus.', 27980), -- Bearers of Bad News
(50356, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A trogg? Hmmm... He may have eaten quite a bit of Azerite to be able to cause all this.\n\nWith him gone, now we can clear out the remaining creatures here and get back to digging! Thank you for your help.', 27980), -- Rock Meet Dynamite
(50352, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Great job! We are going to put this to good use.', 27980), -- Pinch of Azerite
