(50349, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Why aren\'t you wearing a miner\'s cap!? It\'s dangerous out here! Here, put this on.$B$BNow, I got a job for you. Real easy.', 27980), -- An Overrun Mine
